# CC PROMPT — v2.31.6 — feat(ui): Recent Actions audit tab in Logs

## What this does
Surfaces the v2.31.2 `agent_actions` audit table in the UI. Today the endpoint
`GET /api/agent/actions` works but only via curl. This adds a new "Actions"
sub-tab under the Logs panel that shows the audit log with filters, auto-refresh,
and expandable row detail.

Role-gated the same way as the backend: sith_lord + imperial_officer can read;
stormtroopers see a "403 — insufficient role" placeholder.

Two changes:
1. **NEW** `gui/src/components/AgentActionsTab.jsx` — the view
2. **EDIT** `gui/src/components/LogsPanel.jsx` — add the "Actions" sub-tab

